    <title>Caster specific Augs</title>
    <link>http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Veterans&amp;message.id=180524</link>
    <description>&lt;div&gt;I recently have gotten my enchanter 2.0,and was at a loss as to which type of aug to place in the Type 4 slot.I recieved many ideas from fellow guild members,yet all of the replies centered around what would be sub par mana/hp augs with the exception of course to the BiC aug which is too time consuming to undertake imo.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Melee have a plethora of augs to choose from for the type 4 slot on primaries,from drops in zones,LDoNs,DoN wayfarers,DoD.Yet the number of augs which are caster specific is amazingly low,and when these are apparent,they are for type 7/8 slots.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;My suggestion would be for a line of Focus Effect augs which could be placed in the Type 4 slot,or even make a line of focus effect augs which were item type specific but for the &amp;quot;Any&amp;quot; slot.And not just the type V focus effects(Such as mana pres V),but augs such as Murams Vengence,Discordant Ice,Innoruks Irony,etc.This would make items for all classes more unique,giving them a sense that they were tailored specifically for each individual casters needs.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;This also helps the non raiding,casual players needs more specifically as many of the focus effects they seek may not be available to them outside of zones they cant enter.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Combat effect augs for the type 4 slot may in many cases seem nice for some casters,but lets be honest,wizards were not meant to tank mobs that hit for 4k.A 125 point lifetap aug does not help this person stay alive against a mob that will one round them.So either they find the rare 40-50-60 hp aug that can be placed in that slot,or they find a +10 to all resists,or specific stat booster for it.Bic augs are nice,but they are not common,nor are they easy to get outside of a raiding guild who will concentrate on it for each person in guild.&lt;/div&gt;</description>
