&lt;P&gt;It was a sticky situation, and that's why epics are what they are right now. I still don't approve of some of the bigger, more powerful augments being type all (like the BiC and others) since there are items I want to create that use a specific set of augments, but can't, since the type-alls can go into any set and throw off the intentions of that set. It was never really intended for an epic to have more than 500 hps or mana, making it very hard to replace for a good many expansions.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;BR&gt;&#xD;
